T1  - Made to be broken? A theory of regulatory governance and rule-breaking entrepreneurial action
AU  - Lucas, David S.
AU  - Fuller, Caleb S.
AU  - Packard, Mark D.
JO  - Journal of Business Venturing
VL  - 37
IS  - 6
SP  - 106250
